Summary: Walking the dogs,looked up&WTF is that?
divs: Sighting DetailsDogs had to poo,so walked around the block,Waiting for the business,I looked up���iced all the stars,crystal clear,calm night. Cleaned up the mess&glaced up to see a star move from right to left&Back quick. Not a lot,but enough to make me go "Hmmm" Headed home,grabed Blackberry&took Pick,but Not good one,so I dug out the Binoculars&watched it do some strange things. Seemed to move away,then move back. Car drove past&I seemed to change from green to orange&dim quick.That is when I set the Binoculars on the fence to steady&Took photo{Attached}through the right eye peace. 2:13am,let's go see if still there. Yep,and it is doing some freaky stuff,neigbors are even out taking photos.Went back out to get Vid,2:23AM But Clouds suddenly rolled in&it is Headed UP,so it is what it is&what that is,Don't know.
